[ Description ]

  PDF_setfont ( resource $pdfdoc , int $font , float $fontsize ) : bool~

Sets the current font in the specified {fontsize}, using a {font} handle
returned by |PDF_load_font|. Returns TRUE on success or FALSE on failure.


